OL,3,CTeenager dies after serious crash in
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old has died following a
OL,7,Fserious collision near Cardiff.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to The
OL,10,FTumble in St Nicholas, Cardiff at
OL,11,Fshortly after 8pm on Saturday 7th June.
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police confirmed the
OL,14,Fteenager, from the Ely area of
OL,15,FCardiff, died at the scene.
OL,17,FHis family has been informed and is
OL,18,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
