OL,3,CTeenager dies after serious crash in
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FTwo others, a 59-year-old woman and a
OL,7,F64-year-old man, both from Bonvilston,
OL,8,Fwere also involved in the crash and
OL,9,Fwere taken to hospital for treatment,
OL,10,Fafter sustaining injuries.
OL,12,FAn investigation into the cause of the
OL,13,Fcollision is currently underway.
